title: Digital Action Audio Converter v2.6 Incl. Keygen-R2R [ATOM]
description:
Description:
Digital Audio Converter is a powerful all-in-one audio converter for audio conversion and audio CD ripping. Using Digital Audio Converter, you can convert between different audio formats including MP3, WMA, WAV, AAC, FLAC, OGG Vorbis, APE, MPC, SPX, TTA, WV, rip music CD to different audio formats and get information (e.g. Artist, Album, Genre, Track name) from FreeDB, a music compact disc database on the Internet. In addition, the music file tag content (meta data) is also converted.


Features:
Convert
Convert between popular audio formats including MP3, WMA, WAV, AAC, FLAC, OGG, APE and other

Rip audio CD
Rip audio CD to all supported audio formats

Support
Supports M3U, PLS-playlists, Winamp and ID tags

Customize
Customize Digital Audio Converter with visual styles


What's New:
-Bugs fixed when converting between M4A or M4B and other files
-Fixed freezing interface when adding a large number of files
-Minor changes were made in the program's interface
